        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Symphrasites eocenicus gen. et sp. nov. Reconstruction of the forewing venation of the holotype FIS MeI 8384. All unassignable veins are omitted in the drawing. C, costa; CuA, anterior cubitus; CuP, posterior cubitus; MA and MP, anterior and posterior branches of media; pt, pterostigma; R, radius; R1, first branch of radius; Rs, radial sector; Sc, subcosta. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
